{\fn方正苏新诗柳楷简体\fs23}愿死神远离他
<i>may he be released from death.</i>

244
02:11:08,992 --> 02:11:10,191
嘘 小声点
Ssh. Ssh-ssh.

245
02:11:18,138 --> 02:11:23,177
- 我们甩开它了  - 不 它可狡猾了
- We've given him the slip.  - No. He is too cunning for that.

246
02:11:24,994 --> 02:11:28,212
- 那现在去哪儿?  - 西边的警卫室
- So, where to now?  - The western guard room.

247
02:11:28,865 --> 02:11:30,192
可能有路可逃
There may be a way out.

248
02:11:30,758 --> 02:11:34,812
- 那里太高了 没可能逃出去  - 那是我们唯一的机会
- It's too high, there's no chance that way.  - It's our only chance.

249
02:11:36,426 --> 02:11:37,898
我们只能放手一搏
We have to try.

250
02:11:54,486 --> 02:11:55,696
来
Come on.

251
02:12:43,235 --> 02:12:46,752
我听过精灵神药的传说
I've heard tales of the wonders of elvish medicine.

252
02:12:47,128 --> 02:12:49,782
今天有幸亲眼看到了
That was a privelege to witness.

253
02:12:52,263 --> 02:12:53,444
陶瑞尔
Tauriel.

254
02:12:57,596 --> 02:12:58,964
躺着别动
Lie still.

255
02:13:06,229 --> 02:13:08,250
你不可能是她
You cannot be her.

256
02:13:11,812 --> 02:13:13,887
她在遥远的地方
She is far away.

257
02:13:15,891 --> 02:13:22,140
她... 离我很远很远
She... she is far, far away from me.

258
02:13:23,022 --> 02:13:25,553
她行走在...
She walks...

259
02:13:25,553 --> 02:13:29,540
另一个世界的星光之下
under the stars in another world.

260
02:13:33,494 --> 02:13:35,505
只是个梦而已
It was just a dream.

261
02:13:47,261 --> 02:13:50,343
你觉得她爱过我吗?
Do you think she could've loved me?

262
02:13:56,769 --> 02:13:57,974
跟紧一点
Stay close.

263
02:14:07,999 --> 02:14:11,799
到尽头了 无路可走
That's it then. There's no way out.

264
02:14:18,290 --> 02:14:20,363
我们同胞的尸骨
The last of our kin.

265
02:14:24,301 --> 02:14:26,733
他们肯定带着巨大的希望...
They must have come here...

266
02:14:26,733 --> 02:14:30,136
来到这里
hoping beyond hope.

267
02:14:39,121 --> 02:14:41,397
在我生命的最后几天
We could try to reach the mines.

268
02:14:42,510 --> 02:14:44,278
也许我们可以找到金矿
My last few days.

269
02:14:46,536 --> 02:14:48,065
不
No.

270
02:14:50,913 --> 02:14:53,351
我不会这样死去的
I will not die like this.

271
02:14:54,468 --> 02:14:58,005
蜷缩... 挣扎着 奄奄一息
Cowering... clawing for breath.

272
02:15:03,003 --> 02:15:06,418
- 我们引它去熔炉  - 它会看到我们的 必死无疑
- We make for the forges.  - He'll see us, sure as death.

273
02:15:06,418 --> 02:15:08,057
如果我们分头行事就不会
Not if we split up.

274
02:15:08,057 --> 02:15:11,028
索林 我们绝对逃不掉了
Thorin, we will never make it.

275
02:15:11,228 --> 02:15:12,590
也许有人能逃掉
Some of us might.

276
02:15:13,124 --> 02:15:15,732
引它去熔炉
Lead him to the forges.

277
02:15:16,155 --> 02:15:19,427
我们要杀掉恶龙
We kill the dragon.

278
02:15:19,824 --> 02:15:24,452
若一切注定焚尽 那我们也将同赴火海
If this is to end in fire, then we will all burn together.

279
02:15:26,132 --> 02:15:27,314
这边!
This way!

280
02:15:32,173 --> 02:15:35,144
逃吧! 逃吧!
Flee! Flee!

281
02:15:35,344 --> 02:15:38,233
逃命吧!
Run for your lives!

282
02:15:38,233 --> 02:15:43,514
- 你们无处可藏了  - 看你背后! 
- There is nowhere to hide.  - Behind you!

283
02:15:53,039 --> 02:15:54,753
这里!
Here!

284
02:16:25,992 --> 02:16:28,539
{\fn方正姚体}送口信去多尔古多...

285
02:16:28,903 --> 02:16:31,698
{\fn方正姚体}橡木盾到达孤山了!

286
02:16:42,550 --> 02:16:43,518
{\fn方正姚体}去吧!

287
02:16:44,292 --> 02:16:46,281
{\fn方正姚体}你们! 跟我来

288
02:18:51,768 --> 02:18:53,851
这边! 是这边!
This way! It's this way!

289
02:18:53,851 --> 02:18:55,540
来!
Come on!

290
02:18:55,540 --> 02:18:57,031
索林!
Thorin!

291
02:19:01,626 --> 02:19:02,718
跟着巴林!
Follow Balin!

292
02:19:04,570 --> 02:19:05,604
快!
Come on!

293
02:19:21,075 --> 02:19:22,305
索林!
Thorin!

294
02:19:31,645 --> 02:19:33,331
接着!
Hold on!

295
02:20:10,456 --> 02:20:11,992
走! 走!
Go! Go!

296
02:20:15,934 --> 02:20:19,841
这个计划行不通! 这些熔炉是冰冷的
The plan's not gonna work! These furnaces are stone cold.

297
02:20:19,841 --> 02:20:23,678
他说得对 我们没有火能点着熔炉
He is right. We've no fire hot enough to set them ablaze.

298
02:20:26,249 --> 02:20:28,046
我们没有吗
Have we not.

299
02:20:29,175 --> 02:20:31,909
我不觉得你会那么容易以智取胜!
I did not look to see you so easily outwitted!

300
02:20:36,151 --> 02:20:39,161
你年老糊涂...
You are growing slow and fat...

301
02:20:40,116 --> 02:20:42,493
越来越迟钝臃肿
in your dotage.

302
02:20:42,493 --> 02:20:44,625
懒鬼!
Slug!

303
02:20:45,765 --> 02:20:47,810
躲起来 快!
Take cover. Go!

304
02:21:14,757 --> 02:21:17,829
邦博! 让火烧得更猛些! 快!
Bombur! Get those billows working! Go!

305
02:21:32,381 --> 02:21:34,364
比尔博! 上去那儿
Bilbo! Up there.

306
02:21:34,364 --> 02:21:36,490
听我指令 拉那条杠
On my mark, pull that lever.

307
02:21:46,957 --> 02:21:49,415
巴林 你还能配制出闪火吗?
Balin, can you still mix a flash flame?

308
02:21:49,415 --> 02:21:51,285
可以 只需要一会儿!
Aye, it will only take a jiffy!

309
02:21:51,285 --> 02:21:52,285
来!
Come on!

310
02:21:53,651 --> 02:21:55,032
我们没有时间了
We don't have a jiffy.

311
02:22:06,955 --> 02:22:08,462
硫磺在哪儿?
Where's the sulfur?

312
02:22:08,462 --> 02:22:10,187
你确定自己在做什么吗?
Are you sure you know what you're doing?

313
02:22:22,138 --> 02:22:23,534
快点!
Come on!

314
02:22:45,119 --> 02:22:46,314
拉杠!
Now!

315
02:24:42,666 --> 02:24:44,589
引它去众王之廊
Lead him to the Gallery of the Kings.

316
02:25:32,593 --> 02:25:34,896
不要停下来 比尔博! 跑!
Keep going, Bilbo! Run!

317
02:26:20,702 --> 02:26:25,962
你以为骗得了我吗 骑桶者?
You think you can deceive me, barrel rider?

318
02:26:27,510 --> 02:26:30,382
你来自长湖镇
You have come from Lake-town.

319
02:26:31,795 --> 02:26:37,387
这是可恶的矮人和悲惨的长湖人...
This is some sordid scheme hatched between these filthy dwarves...

320
02:26:37,387 --> 02:26:40,057
策划的阴谋
and those miserable tarp trading lakemen.

321
02:26:41,188 --> 02:26:47,519
那些带着长弓和黑箭哭哭啼啼的胆小鬼
Those sniveling cowards with their long bows and black arrows.

322
02:26:48,161 --> 02:26:53,275
也许我该拜访一下他们
Perhaps it is time I pay them a visit. 

323
02:26:53,316 --> 02:26:54,157
不
No.

324
02:26:56,160 --> 02:26:57,889
这不是他们的错
This isn't their fault.

325
02:26:57,889 --> 02:27:00,689
等等! 你不能去长湖镇
Wait! You cannot go to Lake-town.

326
02:27:02,505 --> 02:27:06,555
你在乎他们 对吧?
You care about them, do you?

327
02:27:07,037 --> 02:27:11,866
那就好 让你眼睁睁看着他们死去!
Good. Then you could watch them die!

328
02:27:16,365 --> 02:27:20,660
这里! 你这个无知的废物!
Here! You witless worm!

329
02:27:26,148 --> 02:27:28,313
你!
You!

330
02:27:28,313 --> 02:27:32,132
我要拿回你偷的东西
I am taking back what you stole.

331
02:27:34,792 --> 02:27:40,378
你什么也拿不回去 矮人!
You will take nothing from me, Dwarf!

332
02:27:41,196 --> 02:27:46,040
我打败了你们老一辈的战士
I laid low your warriors of old.

333
02:27:46,040 --> 02:27:50,577
在人们心中植入恐惧
I instill terror in the hearts of men.

334
02:27:51,799 --> 02:27:57,194
我是... 孤山之王
I am King... under the mountain.

335
02:27:57,646 --> 02:28:02,045
这不是你的王国 这是矮人之地...
This is not your kingdom. These are Dwarf lands...

336
02:28:02,817 --> 02:28:05,085
这是矮人之金
This is Dwarf gold.

337
02:28:06,243 --> 02:28:10,532
我们要... 报仇
And we will have... our revenge.

338
02:29:30,241 --> 02:29:35,124
报仇! 报仇!
Ah, revenge! Revenge!

339
02:29:35,932 --> 02:29:41,246
我要让你知道什么叫报仇!
I will show revenge!

340
02:30:17,421 --> 02:30:18,789
听我说!
Listen to me!

341
02:30:18,989 --> 02:30:21,197
你难道不知道是怎么回事吗?
Do you not know what is coming?

342
02:30:23,693 --> 02:30:27,766
我满腔怒火
I am fire.

343
02:30:28,647 --> 02:30:31,783
我... 是...
I... am...

344
02:30:33,365 --> 02:30:34,633
死神!
Death!

345
02:30:43,405 --> 02:30:45,538
我们都做了什么!
What have we done!

346
